ch.unifr.pai.twice.module.client
Class TWICEModuleController

java.lang.Object
  ch.unifr.pai.twice.module.client.TWICEModuleController

public class TWICEModuleController
extends java.lang.Object

Controller for TWICEModules that provides the necessary functionality to manage the lifecycle of a component. The controller logic also handles the lazy initialization of the elements.

Author:
Oliver Schmid
